description: Codie-lyn Kahler has been in the health and wellness industry for over 10 years. Her passion is educating others and empowering them to make the best choices for their families. As a wife, homeschooling mom, and owner of Restoring Wellness Boutique, LLC, she understands the need for holistic services for the whole family. In fact, her passion for wellness started when she helped recover her son, Owen, from a serious medical injury. This ignited a passion to help others and has lead to thousands of lives being changed.  She went on to write a cookbook with her oldest son, Gavin, called 'Be Free: A Family Guidebook to Allergy-Friendly Cooking'. She also authored the booklet 'CBD: Plant-Based Wellness'
